    Anything related to this library's field mapping functionality, which virtually tracks the position of the robot, relative to the field it's on and the objects on said field.
    me.wobblyyyy.pathfinder.frames
    Little snapshots of the field (with the robot), used in collision detection and pathfinding.
    me.wobblyyyy.pathfinder.localizer
    A collection of code related to localizing the odometry functionality of the Pathfinder library.
    me.wobblyyyy.pathfinder.pathfinding
    A rather rudimentary hack at creating an autonomous pathfinding system, capable of operating in both autonomous and TeleOp.
